data.description: Welcome to your charming retreat at Wiggins Lake, where all-sports excitement meets cozy comfort! This delightful 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home embodies the essence of up north vibes, offering a serene escape in every season. Nestled on a generous lot with a large fenced-in yard, this property is perfect for enjoying outdoor activities or simply relaxing on your back deck. Inside, the home features a cozy layout with a touch of charm, providing a warm and inviting atmosphere. Whether you're seeking a weekend getaway or a year-round haven, this cute and simple abode is sure to capture your heart. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make cherished memories in this Wiggins Lake gem!
